OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776715554
OL,3,CPre-school places available in NI 'for
OL,4,Cevery child whose parents want one'
OL,6,FThe Education Authority (EA) has
OL,7,Fpublished a fact file defending how
OL,8,Fpre-school places are allocated in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe EA said 92.43% of children have so
OL,12,Ffar, secured their first preference
OL,13,Fplace for September 2026 and insisted
OL,14,Fa funded place is available for every
OL,15,Fchild whose parents want one.
OL,17,FThey said "no child will be left
OL,18,Fwithout a reasonable local option"
OL,19,Fhowever, first preference places
OL,20,Fcannot be guaranteed for every
OL,21,Fapplicant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
