OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776715554
OL,3,CPre-school places available in NI 'for
OL,4,Cevery child whose parents want one'
OL,6,FThey rejected claims of place
OL,7,Fshortages and added, alternatives are
OL,8,Foffered within a reasonable distance.
OL,10,FThese places will be available within
OL,11,Fa maximum of two miles of the family
OL,12,Fhome for those living in Belfast and
OL,13,FLondonderry.
OL,15,FElsewhere, the range is extended to
OL,16,Fwithin five miles of the family home.
OL,18,FThe EA said admissions criteria is set
OL,19,Fby individual pre-schools and overall
OL,20,Fprovision is sufficient.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
