FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776715554
OL,3,CPre-school places available in NI 'for
OL,4,Cevery child whose parents want one'
OL,6,FThey added "up-to-date application
OL,7,Ffigures, local demand, demographic
OL,8,Ftrends, and accessibility
OL,9,Fconsiderations" are used when
OL,10,Fallocations are being finalised and
OL,11,Fwhere evidence shows pressure on
OL,12,Fplaces.
OL,14,FIn 2025, the EA and Department of
OL,15,FEducation carried out a review on
OL,16,Fallocation numbers for non-statutory
OL,17,Fproviders.
OL,19,FThe EA said they "continue to keep all
OL,20,Faspects of the process under review".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
